              "free_text": [
                " The silicon solid-state detector has a",
                "thickness of about 500 microns. This detector was used",
                "for detecting scattered alpha-particles for laboratory",
                "angles from 20degr to 170degr(29Si) and from 15 degr to",
                "170 degr (30Si). An additional detector of 1500 microns",
                "thickness was mounted to measure value of the",
                "alpha+28Si cross-section at the angle of 40 degr. for",
                "normalization procedure"
              ]
            }
